{"tid":286731,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"WIFI經常斷線求救","createTime":"2017-06-16T20:05:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-17T03:52:39.000Z","uid":29590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"723412ddd49bb54a43a2d84008aa853361763fea","tid":286731,"uid":29590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T20:05:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/17/035320_fbeba388ac02c34bf8061cfebd260689.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F17%2F035320_fbeba388ac02c34bf8061cfebd260689.jpg&h=c8673188&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我係用呢隻LINKSYS ROUTER<br />\n事源係幾個月前開始 (果時用緊舊router)<br />\n上網不論打機睇片MYTYSUPER 樂視 <br />\n全部都會無啦啦斷線 過一陣先連得番<br />\n<br />\n(打機更加唔洗講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 贏變輸唔知比佢害左幾多鋪)<br />\n<br />\n有個例子 我係屋企一向會連住WIFI 食飯前都冇事 咁我冇睇手機擺低左 食完飯望一望  手機信號自動行番4G<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  係手機連WIFI 畫面亦都搵唔到自己個WIFI <br />\n隔左3分鐘到先再要手動連線先搵到 <br />\n<br />\n咁今日Call左寬頻師傅上門睇過 測試唔到問題 留左電話比我話再有事就影比佢睇 <br />\n即晚己經問左佢 佢話係WIFI信號問題 .  要更改信號<br />\n究竟發生咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 為左呢件事已經換左隻Router 又換過d LAN線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最後搵埋人上黎Check <br />\n救命呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92b9fde2c93ef4cf4a9f9a1386a90eede6ae295e","tid":286731,"uid":29590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T20:06:20.000Z","msg":"我以為係ROUTER問題 就換過隻新 點信又係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5281fdf080b9ee9f632621fae2aefd0b95b93855","tid":286731,"uid":29590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T20:07:28.000Z","msg":"以上斷線情況 一個鐘會發生2次以上 完全乜都做唔撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5285df3ce84ec29d66f148754427c90d52932210","tid":286731,"uid":340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci